umc (1.0.4-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Feature: Remove experimental Session Management feature to streamline core experience.
  * Dependency: Remove xdotool dependency.
  * Dependency: Move scrcpy to Recommends to support Snap/Source installations.
  * Fix: Resolve QML property assignment conflicts in DeviceSidebar.
  * Documentation: Add Uninstallation guide to README.

 -- Unified Mobile Controller Team <umc@project.local>  Sat, 03 Jan 2026 10:00:00 +0000

umc (1.0.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Feature: Implement Unified Device API orchestration layer.
  * Feature: Add Desktop launch mode (1920x1080 @ 180dpi).
  * Feature: Add configurable Performance Profiles (Low Latency, High Quality, etc.).
  * Feature: Improve app discovery to list all launchable apps (System + User).
  * Architecture: Refactor backend for improved modularity and consistency.

 -- Unified Mobile Controller Team <umc@project.local>  Sat, 03 Jan 2026 09:10:00 +0000

umc (1.0.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Feature: Add device screen power toggle (ADB).
  * Feature: Add scrcpy screen on/off toggle.
  * Feature: Add audio forwarding toggle for scrcpy.
  * UI: Complete visual overhaul with a professional dark theme.
  * UI: Replaced all emojis with custom vector icons.
  * Fix: Resolved multiple QML warnings and binding loops.
  * Fix: Ensured graceful shutdown of worker threads.

